compute_endpoint.description: Exoscale CloudStack API endpoint (by default: https://api.exoscale.com/v1)

config.description: CloudStack ini configuration filename (by default: cloudstack.ini)

dns_endpoint.description: Exoscale DNS API endpoint (by default: https://api.exoscale.com/dns)

gzip_user_data.description: Defines if the user-data of compute instances should be gzipped (by default: true)

region.description: CloudStack ini configuration section name (by default: cloudstack)

timeout.description: Timeout in seconds for waiting on compute resources to become available (by default: 300)

ip4.description: Request an IPv4 address on the default NIC

ip6.description: Request an IPv6 address on the default NIC

user_data_base64.description: was the cloud-init configuration base64 encoded

healthcheck_path.description: Healthcheck probe HTTP request path, must be specified in "http" mode

healthcheck_strikes_fail.description: Number of unsuccessful healthcheck probes before considering the target unhealthy

healthcheck_strikes_ok.description: Number of successful healthcheck probes before considering the target healthy

healthcheck_timeout.description: Time in seconds before considering a healthcheck probing failed

healthcheck_tls_sni.description: Healthcheck probe set server name for TLS SNI

cpu.description: Number of cpu the Compute instance is running with

created.description: Date when the Compute instance was created

disk_size.description: Size of the Compute instance disk

ip6_address.description: Compute instance public ipv6 address (if ipv6 is enabled)

memory.description: Memory allocated for the Compute instance

private_network_ip_addresses.description: List of Compute instance private IP addresses (in managed Private Networks only)

size.description: Current size of the Compute instance

template.description: Name of the template for the Compute instance

zone.description: Name of the availability zone for the Compute instance

username.description: Username for logging into a compute instance based on this template

id.description: ID of the Network Load Balancer

name.description: Name of the Network Load Balancer

zone.description: Zone of the Network Load Balancer
